name: Merger_alexandra_nichole (not a real person)
description:
I like a reference in my works to guide the look, but the ToS is a bit too particular. i had images removed for cleavage, but i am probably over simplifying the matter. I fully understand this and agree with the need but i do find it to be a little over cautious.

So i decided to make my own person by blending a few inversions to create a consistent look. So i present Alexandra Nichole. Any resemblance to persons living or dead is pure coincidence. tried a few variations to ensure i was variant enough from the originals.

I find some glitching occurring and i know this is not ideal but for my first attempt at making a "person" and kinda pleased.

Heavily nude focussed
